A digital photo frame which fits a small wallet

* 4 connectors on the back and custom USB connector
* light sensor on the back which enables the toggling 
* intergrated solar panel ?
* a fingreprint scanner ?
* black&white display (e-ink ?)
* 16 colors (e-ink/TFT)
* up to 64 pictures 
* 80x40x2 mm - 1-2 mm thickness

Additive circuit printing like NanoDimension's DragonFly can make sense here.


Applications 

* Family photos
* Passwords
* Reminders/calendar


